window.bookSummaryJSON = "No science-fiction/fantasy collection is complete without <i>On a Pale Horse</i>. In this, the first novel of the best-selling Incarnations of Immortality series, Piers Anthony combines a deeply moving examination of the meaning of life and death with a gripping story of romance and loyalty, all set in a world of magic and technical wizardry."; 
